posting_body: ['Property Address', '4610 Lake St East - 417 | Minneapolis, MN 55406', 'Available: 08/05/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', "Sign a lease today and get $1,000 off your first month's rent!", 'This large, rarely-available 2BR  has huge windows throughout the apartment which bring in a lot of natural sunlight and overlook the Mississippi river!', 'Your new home has stainless steel appliances, a stunning granite breakfast bar, & a spacious, adaptable living room.', "You'll also have access to a fitness center and several retail shops right outside of your front door.", 'There is nothing common about West River Commons.', 'Other apartments may boast a great location, and still others convenience and luxury.', 'But a rare few bring it all together in a lifestyle available to anyone.', 'Whether you use West River Commons to relax or energize – or both – you will love to call it home.', 'Live at street level in a two-story rowhouse or overlooking the river valley in one of the best penthouse suites you will find.', 'In addition, standard apartments boast lots of light and modern floor plans which will not cramp your style.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', ' Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'One Heated Underground Parking Space Included in Rent', 'Fitness Center', 'Washer/Dryer in Unit', '24/7 Emergency Maintenance', 'Elevator', 'Pet and Smoke Free Community', 'Access to Retail', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,175', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,195.00', 'Available: 08/05/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
